txt.en: Supply crates can be found at Writhenset in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy supply crates at Writhenset.
Supplies found at Writhenset should be destroyed in order to lessen the strength of your foes within the Wildwood.
Supply crates can be found at Writhenset in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy supply crates at Writhenset.
